'''Michael Stemmle''' wrote the storyline for various [[LucasArts]] projects. He was one of the writers for the video game ''[[Star Wars: Jedi Knight II: Jedi Outcast]]''. He is also credited as a writer for [[Star Wars: Rebel Assault II: The Hidden Empire|''Star Wars: Rebel Assault II'']] and ''[[Star Wars: Battlefront II]]''.

